Kiess ward engineers cannot reset the old druidic marker ring while revenants and greater broken ones keep overrunning the scar perimeter at dusk. Break both threat groups so a repair team can hold position long enough to re-ink the ward lattice.
Engineers held the perimeter through a full mist cycle and re-established the first wardline interval. The forest still shifts, but the repaired markers now give patrol captains a reliable baseline for route triangulation.
